i.   Step1:  Once you access your browser with ``` http://minion-ip/fib/10 ```
ii.  Step2: Request Reaches Nginx 
           Nginx Functinalities:
           ```
           --> Https/URL redirection
           --> Loadbalancing
           --> SSL Termination
           ```
iii. Step3: Once request reached nginx , nginx rediects request to fib service , which is Gunicorn [Python Webserver Gateway Interface HTTP server]
iv.  Step4: Python Program which is running in uWSGI serves the request and return list of fibonacci numbers as per the Logic.

